{"tid":1422592,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我覺得大家要俾返啲肯定俾民間記者會！","createTime":"2019-08-06T11:20:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T16:19:05.000Z","uid":129988,"like":855,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":99,"replies":[{"pid":"a33dfc682241e643de9ef97adeb7f6c47289e250","tid":1422592,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:20:31.000Z","msg":"今日不斷被問佢地嘅代表性<br />\n呢點亦係普遍市民會有嘅質疑<br />\n呢度雖然唔代表全香港人<br />\n但至少我地呢度都要盡力俾到個基礎認受性佢地！<br />\n等佢地聽日可以大大聲話俾全香港人知<br />\n佢地單單喺一個網上平台就代表到幾多人！<br />\n<br />\n正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 民間記者會代表我發聲<br />\n負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地唔代表我地<br />\n<br />\n正負評都好<br />\n都希望大家俾啲鼓勵呢班肯為我地企出黎嘅後生仔<br />\n覺得佢地有不足嘅<br />\n留低你地嘅意見<br />\n俾機會佢地改善<br />\n咁先係我地應該行嘅路<br />\n<br />\n我喺呢度多謝佢地嘅付出<br />\n小弟無以為報<br />\n只能夠無條件支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9203f86a913f53e6080472882bd2d225d4d8c0b","tid":1422592,"uid":129988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:20:49.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"bb6cee1413a5a07fc270cc9994270daae64bd6ee","tid":1422592,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:21:00.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"3ed0fb0b9e0abe0d4d21b4b930e1a27be35d312b","tid":1422592,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:21:30.000Z","msg":"2<br />\n大家正皮plz"},{"pid":"269f46a849c99988c9541b48fb3bc39cc2f2497e","tid":1422592,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:21:55.000Z","msg":"3<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可！"},{"pid":"e4ba182c4617517ed0df32b5aeb1ce75920b35c1","tid":1422592,"uid":272763,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:22:05.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><